  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grass Life Sim is a game in which you can become grass. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game will give you a meditative gameplay. You can stand and contemplate the beauty of the forest around you living your life as grass. You can also perform actions that grass usually performs (stand in the same place). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're grass</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're in the forest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is grass around you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And not only grass</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 game mods: arcade and realistic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful stylized graphics</p></li></ul>",
